                    <span class="text-body"><a href="#" class="border-bottom text-white"><i class="fas fa-copyright text-light me-2"></i>www.velora.com</a> 2025. All Rights Reserved.</span>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-6 text-center text-md-end text-body">
                    Designed By <a class="border-bottom text-white" href="https://www.velora.com">Velora</a>
